From 29e41f53cf40686f08364d9e271bd6b18dc06e65 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: ekane bryan <ekanebryan5@gmail.com>
Date: Thu, 23 Jul 2026 03:02:30 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] feat(ux): compact mobile ticket + admin locations tabs
 (organizer/admin responsive)
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

- Ticket page: compact desktop-like layout on mobile — 2-column ticket
  facts (number/status/type) with full-width location & scan-hint lines,
  smaller responsive text, tighter header (smaller title, QR 112px, less
  padding). Fits without scrolling and no broken text; identical layout
  to desktop, just resized.
- Admin Locations: region/division/city tabs now stack on mobile (were
  cramped at 3-up), 3-col on sm+.
- Audit note: organizer/admin pages are otherwise already responsive
  (stat cards 2-up, EventForm stacks, tables use the view toggle).
---
 .../admin/pages/AdminLocationsPage.jsx        |  2 +-
 .../registrations/pages/TicketPage.jsx        | 22 +++++++++----------
 2 files changed, 12 insertions(+), 12 deletions(-)

